text: Toni Wieser (23 January 1921 - 30 January 1993) was an Austrian ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1948 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1921 births Category:1993 deaths Category:Austrian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Austria Category:Ski jumpers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:People from Bischofshofen
